name: Macosx sdks
body:
MacOSX_SDKs
===========

various MacOSX SDKs

Just in case you have a need or desire to build something using an older version of the MacOS SDK, they can be found here.

Contains the following:
===========

- MacOSX10.6.sdk
- MacOSX10.7.sdk
- MacOSX10.8.sdk
